    <title>关于我</title>
    <link href="/"/>
    <url>/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>欢迎来到小苦瓜的博客，我与于2021~2024在布里斯托大学做修理论统计机器学习与数据分析编程相关内容。同时对算法、应用机器学习、深度学习、大模型感兴趣，博客将不定期更新，关于应用机器学习，深度学习，大模型算法等内容。</p><hr><h4 id="Education"><a href="#Education" class="headerlink" title="Education"></a>Education</h4><p><strong>BSc. Data Science, Mathematics School, University of Bristol</strong><br><em>Sep 2021 – Aug 2024</em></p><hr><h4 id="Experience"><a href="#Experience" class="headerlink" title="Experience"></a>Experience</h4><p><strong>Data Analyst Intern (Dubai - Remote)</strong><br><em>Sep 2023 – Mar 2024</em>  </p><h4 id="Other"><a href="#Other" class="headerlink" title="Other"></a>Other</h4><p><strong>Student Ambassador, Mathematics School Team</strong><br><em>Aug 2023 – Jul 2024</em>  </p><p><strong>Workshop Creator Group, Bristol Data Science Society</strong><br><em>May 2023 – Apr 2024</em>  </p><p><strong>BSc. Data Science Course Rep, Mathematics School</strong><br><em>Apr 2023 – Apr 2024</em>   </p>]]></content>
    
